run_chgres.sh:
This is a script written by George Gayno to change to resolution of siganal 
and sfcanal files with particular care taken to use the correct options for
the surface analysis resolution change.   Runs on cirrus and stratus.

chgdate.f90:
This is a fortran code adapted from Jeff Whitaker's utility scripts to change the date
in the header of the sig and sfc file. This is necessary when forcing the model 
with IAU

chgdateflx.py:
This is a python script used to change the date in the flx files when using IAU
